snippet.title: Twelve Floors Below | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Official trailer for Twelve Floors Below.


You wake up in an elevator with no recollection of how you got there. Where are you? Who can you trust? And more importantly, where are you going and what's down there? 

Twelve Floors Below is a first person, story driven game. The choices you make affect the ending, and once a decision is made, there is no going back. 


The game is soon available on Itch and Game Jolt. 


Want to know more? We have a linktree where you can find our Twitter, Itch, and Game Jolt.


Our linktree: https://linktr.ee/threebuckgames


#gamedev #indiedev #horrorgame
